channel.title: Creating A Small Team For Project
channel.description:
[center][size=12pt][b]DO NOT REPLY IF YOU'RE NOT DEDICATED AND SERIOUS![/b][/size] [center][size=12pt][b]DO NOT REPLY WITH NEGATIVITY OR RUDENESS. KEEP IT TO YOURSELF.[/b][/size]
I'm trying to build a small team for a RSPS project. It'll be 718+. We'll be adding new content / features. I have a moderate / advanced level in java, and basic HTML programming skills. I'd like to have 2 Java developers, me and than someone else. I'll need a GFX / Graphic artist, preferably someone who can do 3D / HD, and I'd like a web developer. I have alot I'd like to do, and already have begun the project, and begun coding. I was just picked up into a RSPS development team, which I also had resigned from due to the lack of owner / other developer dedication.. I'm looking for someone who's serious, and I'm not giving much information just stressing the fact I NEED SOMEONE SERIOUS, and dedicated and looking to go in on a successful project. If you're interested, and want to talk about the server, or my plans, etc comment your skype name please, and I'll be getting in contact with you immediately, I'll let everyone know as spots and positions are filled.
- Thank you In kind regards, Im2High[/center]
